data.description: Welcome Home! This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is located in the Kensey Park section of Canterbury Farms. The main floor features an open plan with a large kitchen with island, huge family room area, and half bath. On the second floor you will find the owners suite with a large walk in closet, & bath with separate shower and garden tub. There are two additional bedrooms, bath and laundry as well. This home has a garage, covered patio, fenced in yard, & sprinklers. Home also has solar panels to save on those high electric bills. Neighborhood has resort style pool, clubhouse, sidewalks and paved walking/biking trails.
